ing%20value%2C%20and%20in%20online%20forums%2C%20he%20saw%20complaints%20from%20people%20who%20said%20they%20regretted%20their%20investment%2C%20bemoaning%20double-digit%20losses%20and%20being%20unable%20to%20sell%20their%20bottles.%20Panic%20set%20in.%20When%20he%20tried%20to%20sell%20his%20own%20wines%20in%202023%2C%20the%20market%20appeared%20to%20be%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinancial%20documents%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20show%20O'Hearn%20sold%20%2415%2C000%20worth%20of%20wine%20at%20a%2010%25%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWine%20funds%20saw%20an%20increase%20in%20interest%20from%20new%20investors%20last%20year.%20Three%20firms%20in%20the%20space%20told%20BI%20that%20newly%20curious%20wine%20buyers%20tended%20to%20be%20younger%20and%20knew%20little%20to%20nothing%20about%20fine%20wine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20influx%20has%20come%20as%20investors%20like%20O'Hearn%20are%20lured%20by%20flashy%20social%20media%20ads%20for%20wine%20funds%2C%20the%20cultural%20cache%20of%20owning%20a%20%2420%2C000%20bottle%20of%20wine%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20potential%20for%20some%20bottles%20to%20see%20stunning%20returns%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20wine%20investing%20is%20tough%2C%20and%20many%20amateur%20investors%20are%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20complexity%2C%20wine%20pros%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECult%20Wines%2C%20one%20wine%20investment%20firm%2C%20says%20it's%20seen%20big%20growth%20on%20its%20platform%20CultX%2C%20which%20offers%20wine%20investing%20to%20a%20retail%20audience.%20The%20firm%20told%20BI%20that%20most%20new%20users%20are%20under%20the%20age%20of%2040.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVinoVest%2C%20the%20wine%20investing%20platform%20that%20O'Hearn%20used%2C%20has%20also%20grown%20in%20popularity.%20In%202024%2C%20the%20firm%20increased%20its%20user%20base%20by%20around%2040%25%2C%20with%20around%2080%25%20of%20those%20users%2030-45%20years%20old%2C%20CEO%20Anthony%20Zhang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20new%20investors%20know%20very%20little%20about%20fine%20wine%2C%20said%20Raj%20Vaidya%2C%20a%20wine%20consultant%20and%20the%20director%20of%20operations%20at%20La%20Paul%C3%A9e%2C%20which%20describes%20itself%20as%20a%20wine%20community%20with%20a%20consulting%20arm.%20He%20says%20participation%20from%20novices%20trying%20to%20play%20the%20market%20has%20surged%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefinitely%20more%20enthusiasts%20who%20just%20like%20the%20idea%20of%20wine%2C%20but%20don't%20really%20know%20very%20much%2C%20who%20are%20now%20interested%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Vaidya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20VinoVest's%20clientele%20fits%20the%20same%20profile%2C%20Zhang%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20new%20investors%20think%20of%20wine%20as%20a%20commodity%2C%20like%20gold%2C%20and%20make%20the%20mistake%20of%20thinking%20that%20wine%20is%20more%20stable%20than%20other%20kinds%20of%20risk%20assets%2C%20Vaidya%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20hasn't%20proven%20true%20recently.%20Cult%20Wines'%20Gearing%20says%20most%20of%20the%20fine%20wine%20market%20has%20been%20in%20a%20downturn%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20a%20broader%20slowdown%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-stocks-chart-shows-bad-year-kering-lvmh-gucci-cartier-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eluxury%20goods%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FTqc7u%2F3%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20wine%20market's%20slowdown%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22527%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Liv-ex%20Fine%20Wine%20100%20Index%2C%20which%20tracks%20the%20price%20of%20100%20of%20the%20most%20sought-after%20wines%20on%20the%20secondary%20market%2C%20is%20down%2024%25%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20compared%20to%20a%2030%25%20gain%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20in%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ddc240e9-ad7e-41ca-a806-8c7457128ddc%5C%22%3EIlliquid%20liquids%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInvesting%20in%20wine%20is%20more%20complicated%20than%20swinging%20by%20your%20wine%20shop%20and%20picking%20up%20what%20seems%20like%20a%20top-tier%20vintage.%20According%20to%20VinoVest's%20Zhang%2C%20a%20wine%20needs%20to%20have%20three%20qualities%20to%20be%20investable.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20needs%20to%20be%20scarce%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20There%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20bottles%20produced%20each%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20needs%20to%20be%20ageable%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20The%20wine%20should%20get%20better%20over%20a%20period%20of%2020-40%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20needs%20to%20be%20brand%20equity%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20relatively%20well-known%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findie-luxury-brands-jacquemus-vampires-wife-seek-investors-close-downturn-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eluxury%20product%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20way%20Rolexes%20and%20Porsches%20are%20universally%20recognized%20as%20high-end.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20pick%20the%20right%20bottle%20and%20time%20it%20right%2C%20typically%20by%20holding%20onto%20the%20wine%20for%20a%20period%20of%20five%20or%2010%20years%20before%20selling%2C%20top-tier%20wines%20can%20appreciate%20as%20much%20as%2015%25%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20navigating%20the%20market%20is%20tough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELa%20Paul%C3%A9e's%20Vaidya%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-people-make-ordering-wine-sommelier-advice-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esommelier%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20high-end%20restaurants%20prior%20to%20consulting%2C%20says%20the%20actual%20supply%20of%20fine%20wine%20is%20a%20lot%20smaller%20than%20investors%20may%20think.%20He%20added%20that%20investors%20he%20works%20with%20are%20frequently%20surprised%20by%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20to%20truly%20distinguish%20a%20%26quot%3Bblue%20chip%26quot%3B%20bottle%20from%20a%20mid-tier%20bottle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20mid-tier%20wines%20are%20prime%20prone%20to%20speculation.%20Things%20like%20good%20press%2C%20a%20cool%20label%2C%20and%20hype%20on%20social%20media%20can%20easily%20jack%20up%20the%20price%20of%20a%20bottle%20before%20it%20quickly%20depreciates%2C%20Vaidya%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20difficult%2C%20frankly%2C%20even%20for%20me%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20in%20the%20business%20for%2025%20years.%20I%20know%20how%20to%20find%20the%20next%20big%20thing%20based%20on%20quality%2C%20but%20the%20next%20big%20thing%20based%20on%20speculation%20is%20difficult.%20It's%20a%20best-guess%20scenario%20most%20of%20the%20time.%20And%20there's%20painfully%20little%20data%20that%20can%20inform%20it%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20mention%20that%20wine%20can%20lose%20value%20due%20to%20numerous%20errors%20that%20occur%20during%20the%20harvesting%20and%20storing%20process.%20Factors%20like%20extreme%20weather%20affecting%20the%20crop%2C%20wine%20being%20stored%20at%20the%20wrong%20temperature%2C%20or%20other%20quality-control%20problems%20can%20essentially%20crush%20an%20investment%2C%20according%20to%20Jason%20Hartman%2C%20the%20president%20of%20wine%20firm%20The%20Sommelier%20Company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20reasons%2C%20many%20investors%20end%20up%20selling%20their%20wines%20at%20a%20loss%20%26quot%3Ball%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Vaidya%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuinessentially%2C%20it's%20kind%20of%20a%20broken%20business.%20It's%20like%2C%20there's%20no%20chance%20that%20they're%20able%20to%20turn%20over%20and%20sell%20all%20the%20sheer%20quantity%20of%20less%20expensive%2C%20less%20fancy%2C%20less%20desirable%20wine%20at%20the%20right%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20some%20newer%20wine%20funds%20out%20there%2C%20which%20tend%20to%20market%20themselves%20heavily%20on%20social%20media%20to%20younger%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20valid%20con%20of%20the%20asset%20class.%20Wine%20has%20very%20little%20liquidity%20until%20it%20reaches%20maturity%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhang%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20believed%20wine%20was%20not%20for%20amateur%20investors%2C%20or%20for%20anyone%20with%20a%20short-term%20outlook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHartman%20actively%20vets%20novices%20who%20want%20to%20get%20into%20wine%20investing%2C%20as%20the%20market%20is%20ultimately%20too%20complicated%20for%20those%20with%20only%20a%20casual%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20aren't%20passionate%20about%20the%20asset%20class%2C%20it's%20best%20to%20stay%20away%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20illiquid%20that%20it's%20just%20not%20worth%20going%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffine-wine-market-investment-returns-alternative-assets-investing-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745755203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680bd69ec6ad288d147f33da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffine-wine-market-investment-returns-alternative-assets-investing-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20market%20for%20fine%20wine%20is%20complex%20and%20illiquid.%20But%20easier%20access%20to%20the%20cloistered%20world%20of%20fine%20wine%20is%20luring%20more%20retail%20investors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40businessinsider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffine-wine-market-investment-returns-alternative-assets-investing-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20Children%20Killed%20In%20Massive%20Fire%20At%20Slum%