insider.com%2Fdeepseek-fuels-nvidia-h200-demand-cloud-cheaper-workload-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20H200%20chips%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20the%20best%2C%20widely%20available%20chip%20that%20could%20handle%20the%20advanced%20model%20at%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20but%20Nvidia's%20inference%20platform%20was%20glitching.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20software%20stack%20called%20Triton%20Inference%20Server%20was%20getting%20bogged%20down%20with%20all%20the%20inference%20required%20for%20DeepSeek's%20reasoning%20model%20R1%2C%20Srivastava%20said.%20So%20Baseten%20built%20their%20own%2C%20which%20they%20still%20use%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%20March%2C%20Jensen%20Huang%20took%20to%20the%20stage%20at%20the%20company's%20massive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gtc-2025-ceo-jensen-huang-ai-landscape-san-jose-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGTC%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20launched%20a%20new%20inference%20platform%3A%20Dynamo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDynamo%20is%20open-source%20software%20that%20helps%20Nvidia%20chips%20handle%20the%20intensive%20inference%20used%20for%20reasoning%20models%20at%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20essentially%20the%20operating%20system%20of%20an%20AI%20factory%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%20onstage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20where%20the%20puck%20was%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20Srivastava%20said.%20And%20Nvidia's%20arrival%20wasn't%20a%20surprise.%20When%20the%20juggernaut%20inevitably%20surpasses%20Baseten's%20equivalent%20platform%2C%20the%20small%20team%20will%20abandon%20what%20they%20built%20and%20switch%2C%20Srivastava%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20expects%20it%20will%20take%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20max.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22efc27361-8adb-455c-838a-ce928b380123%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBurn%20the%20boats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20Nvidia%20making%20tools%20with%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-workforce-growth-chart-pay-gender-revenue-data-20-years-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emassive%20team%20and%20research%20and%20development%20budget%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20match.%20Machine%20learning%20is%20constantly%20evolving.%20Models%20get%20more%20complex%20and%20require%20more%20computing%20power%20and%20engineering%20genius%20to%20work%20at%20scale%2C%20and%20then%20they%20shrink%20again%20when%20those%20engineers%20find%20new%20efficiencies%20and%20the%20math%20changes.%20Researchers%20and%20developers%20are%20balancing%20cost%2C%20time%2C%20accuracy%2C%20and%20hardware%20inputs%2C%20and%20every%20change%20reshuffles%20the%20deck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20get%20married%20to%20a%20particular%20framework%20or%20a%20way%20of%20doing%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Karl%20Mozurkewich%2C%20principal%20architect%20at%20cloud%20firm%20Valdi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20my%20favorite%20thing%20about%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Theo%20Brown%2C%20a%20YouTuber%20and%20developer%20whose%20company%2C%20Ping%2C%20builds%20AI%20software%20for%20other%20developers.%20%26quot%3BIt%20makes%20these%20things%20that%20the%20industry%20has%20historically%20treated%20as%20super%20valuable%20and%20holy%2C%20and%20just%20makes%20them%20incredibly%20cheap%20and%20easy%20to%20throw%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrowne%20spent%20the%20early%20years%20of%20his%20career%20coding%20for%20big%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-twitch-executives-staffers-who-launched-startups-creators-gaming-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitch%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20he%20saw%20a%20reason%20to%20start%20over%20on%20a%20coding%20project%20instead%20of%20building%20on%20top%20of%20it%2C%20he%20faced%20resistance%2C%20even%20when%20it%20would%20save%20time%20or%20money.%20Sunk%20cost%20fallacy%20reigned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20learn%20that%20rather%20than%20waiting%20for%20them%20to%20say%2C%20'No%2C'%20do%20it%20so%20fast%20they%20don't%20have%20the%20time%20to%20block%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Browne%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20mindset%20of%20many%20bleeding-edge%20builders%20in%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20often%20what%20sets%20startups%20apart%20from%20large%20enterprises.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuinn%20Slack%2C%20CEO%20of%20AI%20coding%20platform%20Sourcegraph%2C%20frequently%20explains%20this%20to%20his%20customers%20when%20he%20meets%20with%20Fortune%20500%20companies%20that%20may%20have%20built%20their%20first%20AI%20round%20on%20shaky%20foundations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%20I%20would%20say%2080%25%20of%20them%20get%20there%20in%20an%20hourlong%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229cac925-8f2f-4343-b9c3-4f92b0dcdc3c%5C%22%3EThe%20firmer%20ground%20is%20up%20the%20stack%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20Miller%2C%20CEO%20of%20real%20estate%20investment%20platform%20Fundrise%2C%20is%20building%20an%20AI%20product%20for%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20he%20doesn't%20worry%20too%20much%20about%20the%20latest%20model.%20If%20a%20model%20works%20for%20its%20purpose%2C%20it%20works%2C%20and%20moving%20up%20to%20the%20latest%20innovation%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20worth%20the%20engineer's%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20sticking%20with%20what%20works%20well%20enough%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20That's%20in%20part%20because%20Miller%20has%20a%20large%20organization%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20because%20he's%20building%20things%20farther%20up%20the%20stack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20stack%20consists%20of%20hardware%20at%20the%20bottom%2C%20usually%20Nvidia's%20GPUs%2C%20and%20then%20layers%20upon%20layers%20of%20software.%20Baseten%20is%20a%20few%20layers%20up%20from%20Nvidia.%20The%20AI%20models%2C%20like%20R1%20and%20GPT-4o%2C%20are%20a%20few%20layers%20up%20from%20Baseten.%20And%20Miller%20is%20just%20about%20at%20the%20top%20where%20consumers%20