20made%20%2411%2C572.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20boat%20on%20Stacy%20Spahr's%20Oregon%20property.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680921503fe8d3928363d81b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESpahr%20charges%20between%20%2490%20to%20%24200%20for%20each%20lot.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Stacy%20Spahr%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-monday-21-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emortgage%20payment%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20property%20is%20around%20%242%2C500%20a%20month.%20My%20daughter%2C%20a%20traveling%20nurse%2C%20rents%20a%20home%20that%20sits%20on%20the%20property%20from%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20I%20make%20around%20%242%2C500%20a%20month%20from%20the%20Neighbor%20renters.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20covering%20taxes%20and%20a%20few%20other%20expenses%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20around%20%24500%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20left%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20thousand%20dollars%20a%20month%2C%20free%20and%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b36d97d3-54c3-4a00-811d-74b5767f2c1c%5C%22%3EI'm%20reinvesting%20my%20earnings%20back%20into%20my%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20using%20the%20money%20I%20make%20from%20Neighbor%20to%20supplement%20my%20income%20or%20pay%20off%20debts%2C%20mainly%20because%2C%20other%20than%20my%20house%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20debt.%20I%20work%20in%20insurance%20and%20financial%20planning%2C%20so%20retirement%20savings%20is%20already%20in%20my%20wheelhouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20everyone's%20situation%20is%20different.%20Renting%20out%20your%20yard%20could%20be%20a%20great%20way%20for%20others%20to%20supplement%20their%20income%20or%20save%20for%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20started%20out%20as%20a%20fun%20project%20for%20me%2C%20and%20honestly%2C%20it%20turned%20out%20better%20than%20I%20exp