l%20Airport%20is%20an%20exemplary%20model%20of%20how%20agrivoltaics%20can%20be%20used%20as%20ground-mounted%20solar%20panels%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20CAZRI%20(Central%20Arid%20Zone%20Research%20Institute)%20research%20site%20in%20Jodhpur%20and%20the%20plant%20at%20Sikka%20in%20the%20Jamnagar%20district%20of%20Gujarat%20feature%20slightly%20elevated%20panels.%20Under%20the%20three-metre-high%20panels%20in%20Jamnagar%2C%20lady%20fingers%2C%20%3Cem%3Ecalabash%20%3C%2Fem%3E(bottle%20gourd)%2C%20coriander%2C%20and%20cluster%20beans%20can%20be%20grown%2C%20as%20can%20winter%20crops%20like%20tomatoes%2C%20cucumbers%2C%20zucchinis%2C%20and%20chillies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20model%20stretches%20its%20scope%20by%20increasing%20the%20panel%20height.%20The%20APV%20plant%20at%20Parbhani%20is%20an%20excellent%20example%20of%20this.%20The%20startling%20results%20of%20agrivoltaics%20heighten%20the%20need%20for%20public%20and%20private%20entities%20to%20buy%20into%20the%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAgrivoltaics%3A%20transforming%20farmers%20into%20entrepreneurs%20with%20agency%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReasoning%20why%20farmers%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20view%20agrivoltaics%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Crisky%20affair%E2%80%9D%2C%20Vivek%20Saraf%2C%20founder%20of%20SunSeed%20APV%2C%20part%20of%20the%20team%20that%20launched%20the%20Parbhani%20project%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20risk%20is%20all%20ours.%20Farmers%20are%20stakeholders%20in%20agrivoltaic%20projects.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20get%20a%20better%20income%20than%20they%20did%20earlier%2C%20but%20without%20the%20risk.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20down%20the%20nuances%20of%20the%20model%2C%20Vivek%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20farmer%20typically%20growing%20a%20staple%20crop%20earns%20a%20maximum%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20per%20acre%20per%20year.%20In%20agrivoltaics%2C%20he%20can%20earn%20Rs